# Array sum and average
roast numbers is array[5] ~

roast numbers[0] is 10 ~
roast numbers[1] is 20 ~
roast numbers[2] is 30 ~
roast numbers[3] is 40 ~
roast numbers[4] is 50 ~

roast sum is 0 ~
for i from 0 to 4 toast
    roast sum is sum + numbers[i] ~
nevermind

roast avg is sum / 5 ~

burn "Array sum:" ~
burn sum ~
burn "Array average:" ~
burn avg ~